<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>{{subject}}</title>
    <style>
      body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f5f7fb; color: #0f172a;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; } .container {
      max-width: 640px; margin: 24px auto; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid
      #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; background: #ffffff; } .header { padding:
      24px 28px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; background: #f8fafc; }
      .mark { display: inline-block; width: 42px; height: 42px; border-radius:
      10px; background: #0f172a; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 700; font-size:
      14px; line-height: 42px; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
      .brand { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; } .brand
      strong { display: block; font-size: 16px; } .brand span span { display:
      block; font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; } .content { padding: 28px; } h1
      { margin: 0 0 14px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.25; } p { margin: 0
      0 16px; font-size: 15px; color: #334155; } .details { margin: 18px 0;
      padding: 16px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 10px;
      background: #f8fafc; } .details p { margin: 0 0 10px; } .details p:last-child
      { margin-bottom: 0; } .footer { padding: 18px 28px; border-top: 1px solid
      #e2e8f0; color: #64748b; font-size: 13px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <div class='brand'>
          <span class='mark'>PH</span>
          <span><strong>People Hub</strong><span>Interview schedule</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='content'>
        <h1>{{subject}}</h1>
        <p>Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
        <p>Your interview time has changed. Please use the updated details
          below.</p>

        <div class='details'>
          <p><strong>Role:</strong> {{positionApplied}}</p>
          <p><strong>New date and time:</strong> {{interviewDate}}</p>
        </div>

        <p>Sorry for the inconvenience. Contact the HR team if this time no
          longer works for you.</p>
      </div>

      <div class='footer'>Sent by People Hub recruitment.</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
